data.description: Huge 5bd, 3bth home located in the desirable Sonoran Ranch community with walking paths and park.  Very spacious and open 2 story home with bonus room can be used as den or separate family/living room along with a loft area upstairs.  Kitchen has huge island with granite countertops and upgraded cabinets.  Downstairs bedroom and bathroom are great for guests.  The primary bedroom has a huge walk in closet and double sinks in bath. Laundry room upstairs for convenience.
